episodes.title: Jehovahs Witnesses we are there because we care
episodes.description:
Seeing old time friends is always nice. Being able to reason with them as to your course of action in life is another thing.

Surely looking at jwfacts.com is not dangerous for them ?

episodes.title: Jehovahs witnesses carts Be prepared to defend your faith of those who ask you..
episodes.description:
The "nice " Lady of last time has changed to a "cold lady " oh dear !
They could not defend thier faith but Palmed me off with a card from JW.ORG. Should've used
Rev 19 v 1 to drive home the point as suggested by others.
